productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Lular has one of these. She works as a cake decorator and she says it looks ragged.
My demon loves to play with it.
heard about this on alternative dance radio, decided to give it a try.
This help-desk works quite well. It pointedly improves my golf by a lot.
The box this comes in is 4 yard by 5 inch and weights 12 pound!
